* [irc://irc.gentoo.org/gentoo-soc #gentoo-soc IRC channel] (please be patient, there is not always someone on who can help)
* [mailto:gentoo-soc@lists.gentoo.org gentoo-soc mailing list] ([http://www.gentoo.org/main/en/lists.xml subscription required], [http://archives.gentoo.org/gentoo-soc/ Browse the archives])
